---
title: Herbed Beef & Cheesy Waldorf-Style Salad with Dill-Parsley Mayo & Flaked Almonds
description: This hearty and refreshing salad will not leave you wanting, with tender beef strips, crunchy cos, sweet and crisp apple and nutty flaked almonds. Tossed together with a creamy honey Dijon mayo, this epic combo is sure to satisfy!

